 Hey, I'm across the street, just in case.

280
00:26:57,259 --> 00:26:59,384
I don't want you to get
a false impression,

281
00:26:59,529 --> 00:27:01,829
but you are the only ones
in my room.

282
00:27:18,489 --> 00:27:19,496
Hi.

283
00:27:19,521 --> 00:27:20,932
Lieutenant...will you come in?

284
00:27:20,957 --> 00:27:23,020
Thank you. I thought we could
could have a drink.

