00:27:48,087 --> 00:27:50,832
- What kind of woman are you?
- I am not a monster.

294
00:27:51,349 --> 00:27:52,754
I am sure you like me.

295
00:27:52,925 --> 00:27:55,770
 You don't know anything about me!
You are young and full of life.

296
00:27:55,795 --> 00:27:58,293
Don't tell me that you have never been
you've never been kissed?

297
00:27:58,699 --> 00:28:03,239
Not by some idiot who thinks that a medal
gives him the right to take everything.

298
00:28:03,264 --> 00:28:05,435
Yeah, by a bullshitter who
wasn't taking any chances.

299
00:28:05,775 --> 00:28:08,660
No, he was the most wonderful man
I have ever known.

300
00:28:09,496 --> 00:28:10,822
He had to know how to do it.

301
00:28:11,004 --> 00:28:12,524
What kind of bait did he use?

302
00:28:12,942 --> 00:28:15,118
One thing you couldn't
understand.

303
00:28:18,207 --> 00:28:20,095
 A ring and a promise.

304
00:28:22,879 --> 00:28:24,286
 And now...

305
00:28:28,403 --> 00:28:31,404
It is not because a guy behaved
as a villain that we should...

306
