00:41:35,303 --> 00:41:36,581
Why look for trouble?

449
00:41:37,462 --> 00:41:39,369
Some of us never
never get over it.

450
00:41:39,853 --> 00:41:42,126
I look forward to meeting your wife.

451
00:41:42,314 --> 00:41:43,908
You will like it, it is
is wonderful.

452
00:41:43,939 --> 00:41:47,087
No, no, no, let me
make up my own mind.

