00:41:47,170 --> 00:41:50,883
How about you both come
to dinner at the club with me tonight?

454
00:41:51,413 --> 00:41:53,556
- I take it as an order.
- At 7:00 p.m. sharp?

455
00:41:53,616 --> 00:41:55,298
- We'll be on call.
- All right.

