00:42:26,015 --> 00:42:28,638
Let me introduce you
to the others now.

468
00:42:30,649 --> 00:42:32,145
 Gentlemen. Ladies.

469
00:42:32,175 --> 00:42:34,286
Lieutenant and Mrs. Jack Connell.

